- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: sudoku_grid_constraint_framework|haunted_fabric_of_being_architecture — The structural framework of the Sudoku grid constraint model, where possibilities are defined by overlapping constraints across domains, integrated with the haunted fabric of being architecture — the memetic-physical structure in which knowledge, reality, and time are woven together through recursive tension, spectral overlays, and hauntological entanglements. This structural framework provides the lattice through which emergent knowing becomes possible.

## Z-State

